Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:08.05,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:09.94,sign_194_22_ceiling_sign,T,0000,0000,0000,,Cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:09.94,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:13.44,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It pains me to celebrate the \Nbirth of that guy's son,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:13.45,sign_239_23_store_sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Realty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:15.97,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,but it does sound like a fun event.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:18.19,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tohru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:19.16,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:22.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:27.23,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,I am. I was practicing for the nearby \Nold folk home's Christmas Eve show,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:27.71,sign_616_24_Roast_Chicken,,0000,0000,0000,,Roast Chicken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:29.15,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,but I hurt my leg badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:29.70,Main-Top,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:31.71,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,How frail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:32.99,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:36.22,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,Could you put on a show \Nin my stead, Tohru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:37.26,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:44.98,sign_869_25_white_sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Taxes Included in Prices
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:41.43,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad since the folks in the \Nhome were looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:43.22,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You want us to?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:44.97,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:46.72,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.72,0:00:49.23,Main,Butcher,0000,0000,0000,,You're the pride of our shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:53.20,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:54.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:29.99,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how things turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:31.38,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:32.50,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:37.12,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to help out too, \Nbut right now I've got work...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:39.31,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:41.80,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,and focus on your work, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:44.30,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:49.93,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to call for help \Nfrom my reliable friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:53.18,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:54.51,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:56.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.27,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:58.52,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:03.03,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,I was told I could eat my fill \Nof candy if I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:06.78,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,I even made time in my schedule \Nduring this busy time of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:09.77,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard from Miss Kobayashi, Elma,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:11.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,that you're still useless at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:16.04,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,And that they announced you wouldn't \Nbe useful in this busy period.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:20.26,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I can touch type now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:24.24,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't afford to \Ninterfere with this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:27.40,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're already interfering plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:31.01,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, where's Kanna-san's mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:34.68,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Elma, Miss Kobayashi's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So let's do this on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:38.90,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.02,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:45.52,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,I heard something important was going on, \Nbut we're just putting on a show for humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:48.05,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:49.88,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's watch over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.16,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.41,sign_5543_57_Show_Ideas,Notbeook,0000,0000,0000,,Show Ideas
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:52.40,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:55.28,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,What are we doing for this show?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:59.31,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,It needs to be something \Nthe elderly will enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:02.00,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.13,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,How about an eating contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:06.64,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:07.95,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,A race.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:09.14,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,They might die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:13.13,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,We could play a VR FPS, FFA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:15.64,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, could you speak Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.83,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,All of these ideas require the \Naudience to participate, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.35,0:04:22.36,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't proposed anything yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Do either of you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.81,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:28.99,Main,Sakiawa,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about a play?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:30.69,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,A play?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:34.61,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that thing were \Nhumans act on a stone stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:35.82,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Stone stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:38.62,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,A play sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.12,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:43.87,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,But what play would we even put on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:47.04,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's Christmas,\N why not {\i1}The Little Match Girl{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:49.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's that story about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:54.33,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,On a cold, cold winter night, \Na poor little girl is selling matchsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:58.15,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,None of the people passing \Nby will buy any from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:02.89,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,So in order to warm her chilled body, \Nshe lights one of the matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:08.83,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Then, in the flame, she sees a warm \Nstove and lots of delicious food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:17.01,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,She lights match after match, and eventually\Nher beloved dead grandmother appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.57,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,So the little girl continues\Nlighting her matches
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:22.09,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,to keep her grandmother from disappearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:25.67,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,and the grandmother gently \Nhugs the little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:31.98,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Then the little girl ascends to heaven, \Nembraced in her grandmother's warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:36.01,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit of a sad story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:37.69,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,It's famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.35,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:43.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So what happens to the little girl \Nafter she ascends to heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:46.62,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot. That means she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:50.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. So she strangled her own granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:50.70,Main,Grandma,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.20,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:55.27,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Saikawa, you know so much. I'm amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:57.79,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.99,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go ahead with \N{\i1}The Little Match Girl{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:02.21,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.70,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Will we be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:08.21,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the director, Fafnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:12.21,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'll be directing, \NI won't allow half-baked acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:14.72,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the absolute authority here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.85,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:21.41,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,To be blunt, you're only director by \Nelimination, because you can't act.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:23.14,Main,Luca,0000,0000,0000,,It was a good compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.72,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,First we need to decide on our lead actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:30.11,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Each of you try acting out \N{\i1}The Little Match Girl{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.99,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Number One, Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.80,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:35.11,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Just get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.24,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Don't disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.62,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Matches! Need any matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:42.03,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:45.43,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Are you able to see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:48.50,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,The heartless humans \Npassing before your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.68,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:53.00,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Then your lines will come to you naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:55.38,Italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,Feel it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:58.35,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You foolish, inferior humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.73,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you ignore me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:03.48,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for that crime with your death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:03.48,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Fail. Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:06.47,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Number Two, Elma. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:09.45,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Matches? Do you need any matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.39,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:13.40,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Please! At least hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:16.61,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go back to the office \Nuntil I've sold them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:17.90,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:21.85,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,The salesmen that come to our \Ncompany are always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.74,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hard life. Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:28.25,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,N-Number Three,\NSaikawa Riko. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.33,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:36.35,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.34,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,None of you are any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:42.90,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,We don't really understand your \Ndirecting policy to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.30,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Me, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.23,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:48.48,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Let me be the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.61,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Shouta can be the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:51.22,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:53.31,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:55.23,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Shouta's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:57.23,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Well, leave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.74,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Shouta, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:08.92,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,He looks just like a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.88,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:11.59,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,He passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.88,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's not as cute as Kanna-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:14.88,Main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:15.55,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:18.88,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all planning \Nto achieve by embarrassing me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:18.88,Main-Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,Shouta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.39,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.64,Main-Top,L,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:25.64,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.89,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:30.36,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be better than those two at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.52,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:34.19,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Also, what to do about our lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.49,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:43.12,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:45.28,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Buy some matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.44,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:57.84,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.08,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:01.10,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need any matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:05.59,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:09.35,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,We decided to perform {\i1}The Little \NMatch Girl {\i0}for the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:12.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna was chosen to be our lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.39,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.08,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's incredible, Kanna-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.53,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.49,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to come watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:24.03,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.54,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:28.03,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get through it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.55,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.54,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need any matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:35.05,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,She's most dangerous \Nwhen she gets like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.92,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going to go take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:39.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Matches... Matches...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:39.04,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.30,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.05,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is the Kobayashi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:47.43,Italics,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,It's me. I thought about \Nthe script some on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:50.94,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So you hadn't given up, Mr. Fafnir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:53.89,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come up with then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:52.88,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:57.08,Italics,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,If we stick to the original play, \Nit won't match the current era.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:10:00.07,Italics,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,So I decided to make the \Nlittle girl into a magical girl—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:04.63,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well, time to prepare \NMiss Kobayashi's dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:06.83,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need any matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:20.61,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru. Is there a \Nchimney in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:22.54,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Chimney?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:23.93,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, there isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:28.63,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Saikawa said Santa visits \Nby coming down chimneys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:32.17,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean that old man \Nwho's covered in blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:32.81,Main,Santa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:35.68,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Will Santa be able to come \Nif we don't have a chimney?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:38.57,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:48.51,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.96,sign_15624_206_Episode_10,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 10
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.96,sign_15624_207_Troupe_Dragon__O,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Troupe Dragon, On Stage! (They Had A Troupe Name, Huh)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:57.70,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.09,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.09,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.09,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:07.36,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru! Why would a passerby use \NMiss Kobayashi as reason to refuse her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:10.15,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I be in a hurry \Nif not for Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:10.81,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:15.01,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Lucoa! The grandmother wouldn't \Ntry to warm the girl up naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:17.69,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,But it's warmer this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:20.19,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Fafnir, you're out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:24.01,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,A father would never call his \Ndaughter a "mere human"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:24.90,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:27.94,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you all stick to the script?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:31.82,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of, this story \Ndoesn't have enough depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:35.26,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure we won't bore \Nthe elderly with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.70,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:40.33,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't we try changing it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:42.16,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,What are you suggesting we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.62,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:46.27,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make the story more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:47.59,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:51.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we try mixing in other \Nmyths too, like the kasajizou?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Have it selling hats next to the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:55.35,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,What a mean man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:56.39,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:59.70,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,The main character should be a magical girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:01.57,Main-Top,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:03.45,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,She can obtain the power to burn \Nthis corrupt world to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:06.34,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's nothing from the original left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:10.69,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\i1}47 Ronin{\i0} is popular \Nwith the elderly, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:14.45,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,The one about humans and their quest for \Nrevenge, right? Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:15.86,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:18.38,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,We might as well have some \Nwhile we're at it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:20.89,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:22.53,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make it weirdly sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.83,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Narrator, stop grinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:33.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:36.88,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Santa won't be \Ncoming for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.60,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Does Santa know where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:40.08,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Will he really come?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:41.72,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:45.48,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.37,sign_18372_250_Chimney_Here,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Chimney Here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.37,sign_18372_251_Good__Girl,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Good \NGirl
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.37,sign_18372_252_This_is_the_home,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,This is the home of the\N {\c&H7AEAA5&}good girl, \N{\c&H00CDF9&}Kobayashi Kanna
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.36,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:53.22,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.22,Main,People,0000,0000,0000,,Take home some cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.09,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Did we make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.26,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.46,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:07.43,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, we'll be starting the performance \Nof {\i1}The Little Match Girl{\i0} brought to you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.77,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,by the Oborozuka Shopping District.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.53,Main,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:17.97,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,It was an awfully cold night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:23.48,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,The sun had set upon the street corner, \Nwhere a single young girl was selling matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:28.35,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Matches. Do you need any matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:31.61,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yet no one would buy her matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:33.45,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sell any.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.41,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.75,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Young girl, do you need any hats?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.47,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:43.59,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Before her appeared an old man selling hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:46.09,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,My old wife made these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.80,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,They're very strong hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:49.49,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,W-Would you like one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:51.15,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:53.20,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.26,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:55.97,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,That must be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.42,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Then burn one of \Nthese to warm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:13:59.64,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,They're burning it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:01.10,Main,Takiya,0000,0000,0000,,Even though his wife made it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:04.94,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And they're actually setting it on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:07.74,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,Then something incredible happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:12.61,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,From the smoke there \Nappeared a suspicious man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:14.78,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:17.12,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.59,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,You've been chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:22.26,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,to become a magical girl with a duty to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:24.13,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's this turn of events?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:28.47,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Take it. The power to correct \Nthis corrupt world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:29.88,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:31.09,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That was quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:33.14,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Very good. In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.29,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:37.05,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Please make me a magical girl, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:39.68,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Why do you wish to be a magical girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:43.24,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,To use a magical girl's power\Nto commit vicious deeds
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:47.34,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,and get money to feed my sick wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:50.02,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't think to heal her with magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:53.78,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,You would voice your desires without shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:55.19,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:57.15,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,You are truly human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:06.55,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,This is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.60,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:12.04,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,I only have one staff that will \Nallow you to use your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:15.19,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,You two will have to fight, \Nand the survivor shall receive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:16.24,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.38,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:21.10,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a magic fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:25.47,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let yourself be fooled \Nby that suspicious man's offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:29.85,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you to toy \Nwith the hearts of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:34.41,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:37.09,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just leave you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:38.20,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.55,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:43.67,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,My time with both of you was very enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.79,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It was only a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:50.79,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:53.18,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:56.91,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,A magical girl's role is to cleanse \Ncorruption from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.10,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:04.49,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the rotten people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.74,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,How incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:13.24,Main,Saikawa,0000,0000,0000,,The spell cast by the young girl struck \Na devastating blow to a nearby mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.14,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:22.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, one, two, one, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:26.29,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the ones who set fire to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.25,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who would do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.81,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:32.72,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm didn't mean ill by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.19,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've been a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.81,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Oishi Kuranosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:39.63,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this fire I can \Nsneak into the Kira mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:40.67,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,You have my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.44,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:47.40,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to avenge my lord and claim \Nthe head of Kira Kouzuke no suke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:49.52,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's the {\i1}47 Ronin{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:56.90,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Avenging your lord? How funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:58.53,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,So you show yourself, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.91,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd forfeit your life, then come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:03.25,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:05.44,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,That's the source of the corruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:07.75,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy of magical girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:14.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No one can beat me in this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.39,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn you to dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:21.91,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,They're overdoing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.06,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,If they do that, then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.39,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.63,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Is this that CGI thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.82,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Who you calling a geezer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:29.59,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I said CGI.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.59,Main-Top,E,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:31.85,Main-Top,E,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll have to get serious, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:32.73,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:08.40,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That was incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:16.60,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,How was our play?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:22.87,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:31.18,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It was good. You worked \Nhard all on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:32.38,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:37.41,Main,Take,0000,0000,0000,,Well, care to go out for an after party now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:38.38,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.98,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,I just received a cake in appreciation, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:43.66,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Elma, you're just hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:45.98,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:52.89,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:14.84,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:17.05,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,They just left to head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:20.66,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently they're each having \Ntheir own parties at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.60,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And Kanna-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:24.78,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,She escorted Ms. Saikawa home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:26.29,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:28.29,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:31.05,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Or would you like to go to bed as is today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:34.90,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since it is Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:45.94,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:48.08,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're not cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:49.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.32,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:54.19,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You asking to see the view at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.08,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:56.59,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:19:59.84,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:02.50,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What? A Christmas present?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:03.38,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:07.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I got you some medicine that \Nworks well for lower back pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:08.45,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.13,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:15.51,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's a valuable item in the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:18.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You grind it down and\Napply it to your lower back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:19.51,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It works perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:22.45,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:27.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I was worried all day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:29.45,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:34.05,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I was full of \Nanxiety as I watched your play,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:37.01,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,worrying when I should \Njump in to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.72,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:44.72,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You really did a nice job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:45.73,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:48.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:05.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's a White Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:09.51,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Here! A Christmas present from me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:10.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:11.79,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:15.52,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:18.12,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:25.12,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru, settle down! I'll fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.44,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.46,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get close!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:26.21,sign_33686_412_Big_End_of__Year,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Big End of\N Year Sale
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:26.21,sign_33686_413_Oborozuka__Shopp,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Oborozuka \NShopping \NDistrict
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:27.97,sign_33686_411_Next_Episode,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,271)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.96,0:23:29.50,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fafnir, that was quite the \Nexcellent performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:30.34,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:31.63,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic human.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:32.79,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:34.93,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Why do you wish to be a magical girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:35.79,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mimic me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:36.59,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:39.97,sign_33950_422_Episode_11,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(276,1)}Episode 11
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:39.97,sign_33950_423_Year_End__New_Ye,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(376,1)}Year End, New Year! (No Comiket Bit This Time)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.59,0:23:38.22,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You are truly human.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:39.37,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
